(stouter,stoutest) 

1. ADJ A stout person is rather fat. 肥胖的 

例： He was a tall, stout man with grey hair. 他是一个又高又胖、满头银发的男子。 

2. ADJ Stout shoes, branches, or other objects are thick and strong. (鞋、枝条等物体) 结实的 

例： I hope you've both got stout shoes. 我希望你们两个都穿结实的鞋。

